                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "j7AM5",
                  "fill": "#94a3b8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Entry: IntersectionObserver triggers. Digits cycle 0-9 randomly, then lock L→R with 150ms stagger. White flash on lock. Status label: RESOLVING → LOCKED.\n\nHover: Digits decompose into machine notation (3800+ → 3.8e3, 500+ → 5.0e2, 25 → 0x19). Mouseout reassembles.\n\nGhost segments: inactive LCD segments at 6% opacity show full \"8\" skeleton behind active digit.\n\nReduced-motion: skip cycling, show final value with fade-in.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
