                  "fontSize": 10,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "letterSpacing": 3
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "TSFYX",
                  "fill": "#94a3b8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Entry: Carrier pulse (bright dot) travels down the backplane line. As it passes each card, nodes spawn outward from center with scale(0→1) + edges draw via stroke-dashoffset. 200ms stagger between cards.\n\nHover: Hovering one card sends a muted pulse through the other two — cross-card connecting lines briefly flash at 30% opacity. Label shows CROSS_REF: LINKED_SYSTEMS.\n\nBackplane: Thin vertical line runs behind all 3 cards, gradient shifts per-card accent. Represents the shared data bus.\n\nReduced-motion: static constellation, no pulse travel.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
